Requests Per Second (RPS)
sum(rate(http_server_requests_seconds_count[1m])) by (uri)

p95 Latency
histogram_quantile(0.95, sum(rate(http_server_requests_seconds_bucket[1m])) by (le))

Error rate
100 * sum(rate(http_server_requests_seconds_count{status=~"4..|5.."}[1m]))
/
sum(rate(http_server_requests_seconds_count[1m]))

CPU usage
100 * avg(process_cpu_usage{job="springboot-app"})

Heap usage
100 *
sum(
  jvm_memory_used_bytes{
    area="heap",
    job="springboot-app"
  }
) by (instance)
/
sum(
  jvm_memory_max_bytes{
    area="heap",
    job="springboot-app"
  }
) by (instance)

HikariCP Active Connections (Currently active DB connections)
100 * hikaricp_connections_active / hikaricp_connections_max
